{"tid":2259731,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"發唔發覺每次用筷子食飯都好大壓力","createTime":"2020-10-27T05:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T17:23:31.000Z","uid":34147,"like":185,"dislike":287,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"fae378e3fa867147c59f165ab47cf7be50bb25ec","tid":2259731,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:00:13.000Z","msg":"筷子 -  一種會令人抑鬱症嘅餐具<br />\n當一枱人食飯要夾餸時, 就其夾d 圓或者滑嘅東西 (e.g. 春卷/冬菇）<br />\n一夾起就feel 到d 件餸慢慢喺筷子流走中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要即刻計算件餸離自己隻碗嘅距離同時間去判斷究竟拎走件餸定重新夾過穩定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一但估算錯誤件餸就會跌落枱面柒到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一個情況就係夾極都夾唔起<br />\n夾唔起一次好正常<br />\n夾唔起兩次都可以<br />\n夾唔起三次自己就會開始緊張， 同枱人亦都會開始注意到你<br />\n就喺呢個時間，你要選擇認低威拎匙羹（如有）定係繼續重試<br />\n當重試嘅時候就要不斷調較大力d 好定細力d 好<br />\n如果繼續重試都失敗嘅話<br />\n同枱人就會彈出一句「我幫你夾啦」即刻全枱靜哂<br />\n你亦都搏唔刀咁回句「唔該」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時自己食飯都唔好受<br />\n就其係食麵嘅時候<br />\n一夾起一住上黎嘅時候突然彈彈彈彈彈彈<br />\n輕則彈副自己成面係<br />\n重則彈到隔黎位 唯有講聲唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者夾餸時， 就其係重嘅野，如雞翼/羅白<br />\n一冼手成件跌返落碗湯度<br />\n有如肥婆跳水d 水花彈哂上黎一樣成身係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解現代人普遍長命過古人咁多？<br />\n因為古人好多時都抑鬱死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e4f7f0a25ea4d0432039ba8cc5f918f1a39f1c","tid":2259731,"uid":13361,"like":147,"dislike":7,"score":140,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:01:56.000Z","msg":"筷子係用嚟拮嘢食㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71026bb95719563ae7265b028b31ddc552e44bd6","tid":2259731,"uid":158372,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:02:10.000Z","msg":"夾唔到嘢會覺得好撚失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3c1b82c36801498a9018865f0884f1ecb7eece","tid":2259731,"uid":6752,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:02:53.000Z","msg":"係薯粉先食"},{"pid":"189c3869e6f1208bbb7ded425a4f8402f64e8fd5","tid":2259731,"uid":101845,"like":100,"dislike":0,"score":100,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:03:11.000Z","msg":"法國好多人唔識揸筷子"},{"pid":"be7b2cc2a7592b44f035b49dc752d5b26954e1ff","tid":2259731,"uid":6752,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:03:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係食薯粉先大壓力</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f703b2d0612fe4b616353123929491b6b71c6bb1","tid":2259731,"uid":62,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:03:57.000Z","msg":"試過同藍絲食飯嬲得制整斷咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21afe6480388f9fad69adb05ebbac8f2057e831","tid":2259731,"uid":33359,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"夾瀨粉先叫大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d55f8c453951ee1ee91f351f4fb3f2338eae84","tid":2259731,"uid":321194,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"189c3869e6f1208bbb7ded425a4f8402f64e8fd5","tid":2259731,"uid":101845,"like":100,"dislike":0,"score":100,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:03:11.000Z","msg":"法國好多人唔識揸筷子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f0693db6c26ceeb945214fd2ea1253f19246754","tid":2259731,"uid":109629,"like":53,"dislike":7,"score":46,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:06:34.000Z","msg":"我細細個自學揸筷子, 唔知點樣學壞手勢用左無名指同尾指夾, 正常人係用中指同食指<br />\n<br />\n而家成日俾人見到就笑鳩我唔識揸筷子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚煩, 我夾野夾得好地地你理鳩我用腳指夾咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c454b237fc22da551eba9401ed0b91143fc9159","tid":2259731,"uid":30524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"sco